{"tha-ap107:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap107:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap107:0.3":"Mutthipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap107:1.1":"“Sudassanoti namena, ","tha-ap107:1.2":"malakaro aham tada; ","tha-ap107:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap107:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap107:2.1":"Jatipuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap107:2.2":"pujayim padumuttaram; ","tha-ap107:2.3":"Visuddhacakkhu sumano, ","tha-ap107:2.4":"dibbacakkhum samajjhagam. ","tha-ap107:3.1":"Etissa pupphapujaya, ","tha-ap107:3.2":"cittassa panidhihi ca; ","tha-ap107:3.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap107:3.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap107:4.1":"Solasasimsu rajano, ","tha-ap107:4.2":"devuttarasanamaka; ","tha-ap107:4.3":"Chattimsamhi ito kappe, ","tha-ap107:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap107:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap107:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap107:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap107:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mutthipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap107:7.1":"Mutthipupphiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}